Package com.amazon.pages

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BookDetailsPage
    BookDetailsPage implements logic to get all book details
    BuyingChoicesPage
    BuyingChoicesPage implements logic for different offers from sellers as per condition of book
    HomePage
    HomePage class implements search criteria by scope on Amazon.com Home page
    KindleDetailsTab
    KindleDetailsTab class is used to get all information related to Kindle edition of book including cost,pages,settings and supported devices
    OfferListingDetailsPage
    OfferLisitngDetailsPage implements logic to get all offers from different Sellers
    PaperBackDetailsTab
    PaperBackDetailsTab class is used to get all information related to PaperBack edition of book including cost range,starting cost based on new books,used books and rental books
